snippet.textDisplay:
nigāh-e-yār jise āshnā-e-rāz kare. 
vo apnī ḳhūbi-e-qismat pe kyuuñ na naaz kare

what a beautiful Ghazal Abbida jee tapped into with the opening line of that hauntingly beautiful poetry.  the very next verse goes, 

diloñ ko fikr-e-do-ālam se kar diyā āzād
 tire junūñ kā ḳhudā silsila darāz kare

talk about profound !!! 

i would highly recommend reading this entire ghazal.
